### Register Admin User
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/Authentication/RegisterAdministrator
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Admin",
  "lastName": "User",
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "Admin123!",
  "email": "admin@cinemax.com"
}

###

### Register Regular Buyer User
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/Authentication/RegisterBuyer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "username": "johndoe",
  "password": "Buyer123!",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com"
}

