### Login as Admin
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/Authentication/Login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

###

### Login as Buyer
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/Authentication/Login
