### Get All Users (Requires Admin Token)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/User/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Get User by Username (Requires Admin or Owner)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/User/users/admin
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

